overview: Exciting, fact-filled squirrel hunting and calling tips, including: * How, when and proper sounds of squirrel calling * Where to find squirrels * Exciting squirrel dog hunting * The habits of grey squirrels vs. fox squirrels * The kinds of gun & ammunition to start the youth squirrel hunter
tagline: "He Couldn't Help But Give Away His Location"
title: The Magic of Squirrel Calling
